#. <section class="sutta" id="sn36.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn36.12:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 36"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 36"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.12:0.2"
msgid "2. Rahogatavagga"
msgstr "2. In Private"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn36.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Paṭhamaākāsasutta"
msgstr "12. In the Sky (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn36.12:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ākāse vividhā vātā vāyanti."
msgstr "“Mendicants, various winds blow in the sky."

msgctxt "sn36.12:1.2"
msgid ""
"Puratthimāpi vātā vāyanti, pacchimāpi vātā vāyanti, uttarāpi vātā vāyanti, "
"dakkhiṇāpi vātā vāyanti, sarajāpi vātā vāyanti, arajāpi vātā vāyanti, sītāpi "
"vātā vāyanti, uṇhāpi vātā vāyanti, parittāpi vātā vāyanti, adhimattāpi vātā "
"vāyanti."
msgstr ""
"Winds blow from the east, the west, the north, and the south. There are "
"winds that are dusty and dustless, cool and warm, weak and strong."

msgctxt "sn36.12:1.3"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, imasmiṃ kāyasmiṃ vividhā vedanā uppajjanti, sukhāpi "
"vedanā uppajjati, dukkhāpi vedanā uppajjati, adukkhamasukhāpi vedanā "
"uppajjatīti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, various feelings arise in this body: pleasant, painful, and "
"neutral feelings."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn36.12:2.1"
msgid "Yathāpi vātā ākāse,"
msgstr "There are many and various"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:2.2"
msgid "vāyanti vividhā puthū;"
msgstr "winds that blow in the sky."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:2.3"
msgid "Puratthimā pacchimā cāpi,"
msgstr "From the east they come, also the west,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:2.4"
msgid "uttarā atha dakkhiṇā."
msgstr "the north, and then the south."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn36.12:3.1"
msgid "Sarajā arajā capi,"
msgstr "They are dusty and dustless,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:3.2"
msgid "sītā uṇhā ca ekadā;"
msgstr "cool and sometimes warm,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:3.3"
msgid "Adhimattā parittā ca,"
msgstr "strong and weak;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:3.4"
msgid "puthū vāyanti mālutā."
msgstr "these are the different breezes that blow."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn36.12:4.1"
msgid "Tathevimasmiṃ kāyasmiṃ,"
msgstr "So too, in this body"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:4.2"
msgid "samuppajjanti vedanā;"
msgstr "feelings arise,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:4.3"
msgid "Sukhadukkhasamuppatti,"
msgstr "pleasant and painful,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:4.4"
msgid "adukkhamasukhā ca yā."
msgstr "and those that are neutral."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn36.12:5.1"
msgid "Yato ca bhikkhu ātāpī,"
msgstr "But when a mendicant is keen,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: sampajaññaṃ na riñcati → sampajāno nirujjhati (s1-3) | sampajāno nirūpadhi (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn36.12:5.2"
msgid "sampajaññaṃ na riñcati;"
msgstr "not neglecting situational awareness,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:5.3"
msgid "Tato so vedanā sabbā,"
msgstr "that astute person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:5.4"
msgid "parijānāti paṇḍito."
msgstr "understands all feelings."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn36.12:6.1"
msgid "So vedanā pariññāya,"
msgstr "Completely understanding feelings,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:6.2"
msgid "diṭṭhe dhamme anāsavo;"
msgstr "they’re without defilements in this very life."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:6.3"
msgid "Kāyassa bhedā dhammaṭṭho,"
msgstr "That knowledge-master is grounded in the teaching;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.12:6.4"
msgid "saṅkhyaṃ nopeti vedagū”ti."
msgstr "when their body breaks up, they can’t be reckoned.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn36.12:6.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
